{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.011.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance au milieu des \u00e9preuves, \u00e0 l\u2019exemple de J\u00e9sus-Christ<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-3: cf. (1 Co 9:24-27. Ph 3:11-14.) (Ph 2:5-11. 1 Pi 2:21-24; 4:12, 13.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Nous donc aussi, puisque nous sommes environn\u00e9s d\u2019une si grande nu\u00e9e de t\u00e9moins, rejetons tout fardeau, et le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qui nous enveloppe si facilement, et courons avec pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance dans la carri\u00e8re qui nous est ouverte,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.11.40","name":"H\u00e9breux 11:40","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.11.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>ayant les regards sur J\u00e9sus, le chef et le consommateur de la foi, qui, en vue de la joie qui lui \u00e9tait r\u00e9serv\u00e9e, a souffert la croix, m\u00e9pris\u00e9 l\u2019ignominie, et s\u2019est assis \u00e0 la droite du tr\u00f4ne de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Consid\u00e9rez, en effet, celui qui a support\u00e9 contre sa personne une telle opposition de la part des p\u00e9cheurs, afin que vous ne vous lassiez point, l\u2019\u00e2me d\u00e9courag\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.005,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 4-11: cf. (Pr 3:11, 12. Ap 3:19.) (Ps 119:67, 71. 1 Pi 1:6, 7.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>\n    Vous n\u2019avez pas encore r\u00e9sist\u00e9 jusqu\u2019au sang, en luttant contre le p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et vous avez oubli\u00e9 l\u2019exhortation qui vous est adress\u00e9e comme \u00e0 des fils:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Mon fils, ne m\u00e9prise pas le ch\u00e2timent du Seigneur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">et ne perds pas courage lorsqu\u2019il te reprend;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>car le Seigneur ch\u00e2tie celui qu\u2019il aime,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">et il frappe de la verge tous ceux qu\u2019il reconna\u00eet pour ses fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Supportez le ch\u00e2timent: c\u2019est comme des fils que Dieu vous traite; car quel est le fils qu\u2019un p\u00e8re ne ch\u00e2tie pas?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mais si vous \u00eates exempts du ch\u00e2timent auquel tous ont part, vous \u00eates donc des enfants ill\u00e9gitimes, et non des fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>D\u2019ailleurs, puisque nos p\u00e8res selon la chair nous ont ch\u00e2ti\u00e9s, et que nous les avons respect\u00e9s, ne devons-nous pas \u00e0 bien plus forte raison nous soumettre au P\u00e8re des esprits, pour avoir la vie?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Nos p\u00e8res nous ch\u00e2tiaient pour peu de jours, comme ils le trouvaient bon; mais Dieu nous ch\u00e2tie pour notre bien, afin que nous participions \u00e0 sa saintet\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il est vrai que tout ch\u00e2timent semble d\u2019abord un sujet de tristesse, et non de joie; mais il produit plus tard pour ceux qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 ainsi exerc\u00e9s un fruit paisible de justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La sanctification. Pr\u00e9ceptes divers<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-17: cf. (1 Pi 3:11, 12; 1:13-17. Ap 21:27.) (Ge 25:29-34; 27:30-38.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\n    Fortifiez donc vos mains languissantes et vos genoux affaiblis;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et suivez avec vos pieds des voies droites, afin que ce qui est boiteux ne d\u00e9vie pas, mais plut\u00f4t se raffermisse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Recherchez la paix avec tous, et la sanctification, sans laquelle personne ne verra le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.15","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:15","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Veillez \u00e0 ce que nul ne se prive de la gr\u00e2ce de Dieu; \u00e0 ce qu\u2019aucune racine d\u2019amertume, poussant des rejetons, ne produise du trouble, et que plusieurs n\u2019en soient infect\u00e9s;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.16","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:16","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il n\u2019y ait ni impudique, ni profane comme \u00c9sa\u00fc, qui pour un mets vendit son droit d\u2019a\u00eenesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.17","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:17","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Vous savez que, plus tard, voulant obtenir la b\u00e9n\u00e9diction, il fut rejet\u00e9, quoiqu\u2019il la sollicit\u00e2t avec larmes; car son repentir ne put avoir aucun effet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.18","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:18","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-29: cf. (Ex 19:10-25; 20:1-19.) (Ga 4:26. Ap 3:12; 21:2, 3; 5:11, 12. \u00c9p 1:10.) (H\u00e9 2:1-3; 10:26-35.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Vous ne vous \u00eates pas approch\u00e9s d\u2019une montagne qu\u2019on pouvait toucher et qui \u00e9tait embras\u00e9e par le feu, ni de la nu\u00e9e, ni des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres, ni de la temp\u00eate,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.19","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:19","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>ni du retentissement de la trompette, ni du bruit des paroles, tel que ceux qui l\u2019entendirent demand\u00e8rent qu\u2019il ne leur en f\u00fbt adress\u00e9 aucune de plus,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.20","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:20","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>car ils ne supportaient pas cette d\u00e9claration: Si m\u00eame une b\u00eate touche la montagne, elle sera lapid\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.21","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:21","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et ce spectacle \u00e9tait si terrible que Mo\u00efse dit: Je suis \u00e9pouvant\u00e9 et tout tremblant!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.22","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:22","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais vous vous \u00eates approch\u00e9s de la montagne de Sion, de la cit\u00e9 du Dieu vivant, la J\u00e9rusalem c\u00e9leste, des myriades qui forment le ch\u0153ur des anges,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.23","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:23","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>de l\u2019assembl\u00e9e des premiers-n\u00e9s inscrits dans les cieux, du juge qui est le Dieu de tous, des esprits des justes parvenus \u00e0 la perfection,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.24","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:24","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>de J\u00e9sus qui est le m\u00e9diateur de la nouvelle alliance, et du sang de l\u2019aspersion qui parle mieux que celui d\u2019Abel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.25","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:25","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Gardez-vous de refuser d\u2019entendre celui qui parle; car si ceux-l\u00e0 n\u2019ont pas \u00e9chapp\u00e9 qui refus\u00e8rent d\u2019entendre celui qui publiait les oracles sur la terre, combien moins \u00e9chapperons-nous, si nous nous d\u00e9tournons de celui qui parle du haut des cieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.26","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:26","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>lui, dont la voix alors \u00e9branla la terre, et qui maintenant a fait cette promesse: Une fois encore j\u2019\u00e9branlerai non seulement la terre, mais aussi le ciel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.27","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:27","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Ces mots: Une fois encore, indiquent le changement des choses \u00e9branl\u00e9es, comme \u00e9tant faites pour un temps, afin que les choses in\u00e9branlables subsistent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.28","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.28","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:28","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.012.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, recevant un royaume in\u00e9branlable, montrons notre reconnaissance en rendant \u00e0 Dieu un culte qui lui soit agr\u00e9able, avec pi\u00e9t\u00e9 et avec crainte,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.29","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.12.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.12.29","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 12:29","prev_osis_id":"Heb.012.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.013.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.12.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>car notre Dieu est aussi un feu d\u00e9vorant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.13.1","n